title: PPPP’s Rais Nabeel Ahmed wins PP-267 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 10 (APP): Pakistan Peoples Party Parliamentarian (PPPP), Rais Nabeel Ahmad has won the Punjab Assembly election from PP-267, Rahim Yar Khan-XIII by securing 46,483 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Rais Muhammad Hamza, an independent candidate who bagged 26,785 votes.
Overall voters’ turn-out remained 50.13%.
